{"tid":1153252,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【貿易戰爆發】中國還擊 1/6對美國商品加稅率 最高達25%","createTime":"2019-05-13T13:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T13:59:45.000Z","uid":138232,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fac740eabe951e03d382d68223ee071fcf144744","tid":1153252,"uid":138232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:25:00.000Z","msg":"中國國務院今日晚上在網站宣佈，將於6月1日凌晨零時起，對已經徵收關稅、價值600億美元（約4,680億港元）的美國商品，提高關稅的稅率，將分別以25%、20%或10%徵稅；之前稅率為5%的商品，關稅則維持不變。<br />\n<br />\n中方指，這次調整美國貨品的關稅稅率，是回應美方單邊主義、貿易保護主義，中方希望，美方回到雙邊經貿磋商的正確軌道，和中方共同努力，相向而行，爭取在相互尊重的基礎上達成一個互利雙贏的協議。"},{"pid":"2f6f2d642d49363ecd8c4fab05de685bd45bc6a8","tid":1153252,"uid":12670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:25:21.000Z","msg":"利好消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7896431b34fe8b5de0f6bc77fb6266e3f0bc4162","tid":1153252,"uid":138232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:25:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190513/59596997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190513%2F59596997&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT3vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=df2251d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190513%2F59596997&h=b3e7adb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190513/59596997</a>"},{"pid":"9be2892bd86f052ec4da6960ec0528ced0bc83fb","tid":1153252,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:26:57.000Z","msg":"支那西快投降啦 屌你老母西"},{"pid":"7de3104189456d9293fdfb51781dad9d64111259","tid":1153252,"uid":138232,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Oyp4Yz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Oyp4Yz.png&h=3ddec9e0